<dl id="n12112c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12112c">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12112c"> 112(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> sickle tonsure (Norma)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">La vie &eacute;tait rude, que menaient dans ces clo&icirc;tres ces hommes s&eacute;par&eacute;s du si&egrave;cle et marqu&eacute; sur le front d&apos;une tonsure en forme de croissant. <br>[It was a harsh life that these men led in these cloisters, separated from their time and marked on their brow with a <mark>tonsure in the shape of a crescent</mark>. <small> <a name="STCM" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STCM"><cite title="source">Saint Colomban</cite></a> (1905) 4</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
